org.araneaframework.http
Interface StateVersioningContext

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
StandardStateVersioningFilterWidget
public interface StateVersioningContext
extends Serializable

Interface of a component hierarchy state versioning filter. This allows to support client-side history navigation by storing the versioned hierarchies between requests.

Since:
1.2
Author:
Taimo Peelo (taimo@araneaframework.org)

expire

void expire()
Expires all stored versioned states. Should be called when current flow has completed some truly irreversible operation -- i.e calling remote service to bill a credit card etc etc.
